# Project Overview

Lerna-managed monorepo of `@ascua/*` Ember addons used by the Hire Insight platform. Provides reusable UI components, integrations, and utilities.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Ember.js (addon format)
- **Monorepo:** Lerna with npm
- **Build:** ember-cli

## Key Commands

- `make setup` — Install dependencies (do NOT use `npm install` directly)
- `make clean` — Clean all node_modules and build artifacts
- `make serve` — Start development server
- `make version` — Version packages
- `make publish` — Publish to npm

See `development-setup.mdc` for detailed dependency management instructions.
